        "configs": "Sprite sheet configs (JSON). One per sheet, defines animations, segments, frame counts.",
        "scenes": "Blender scene files (.blend). One per sheet, contains NLA setup, camera, hair physics.",
        "renders": "Output. Per sheet: individual frames in subfolder, assembled PNG sprite sheet, GIF preview."
    },

